Class NoopDatasetStateStore

  • java.lang.Object

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DatasetStateStore<JobState.DatasetState>, StateStore<JobState.DatasetState>

    public class NoopDatasetStateStore
extends FsDatasetStateStore
    An extension of FsDatasetStateStore where all operations are noop. Used to disable the state store.
